description: Feed the family with tasty honey soy chicken skewers, and save time with a ready-made crunchy broccoli slaw.
keywords: Skewer & kebab,Quick & easy dinner,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Quick & easy lunch,Dinner Made Easy,Chicken,Sesame free,Dairy free
name: Quick Chicken Skewers Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 375g bottle Masterfoods honey soy garlic marinade
1kg chicken breast fillets, sliced into 1cm-wide strips

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat a barbecue or chargrill pan over medium-high heat. Combine chicken with three-quarters of the marinade in a large bowl and toss to coat.
Grease barbecue or chargrill with the olive oil, then grill skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, or until charred and cooked through. Baste skewers with remaining marinade while cooking.
In a bowl, toss the broccoli slaw together with the dressing and cranberries from the kit, then divide among plates and top with skewers. Drizzle over garlic sauce to serve.
